WEBVTT

00:00.601 --> 00:02.601
thing.

00:02.737 --> 00:04.403
This is about me
making my own money!

00:04.405 --> 00:06.405
Well, then go get a real job
like real people.

00:06.473 --> 00:08.273
You've always known
who I am!
Yeah.

00:08.543 --> 00:10.443
But I didn't know you'd also be
a shitty mother.

00:11.812 --> 00:13.078
Got an idea for a job.

00:13.147 --> 00:15.614
Uh, you know
what a hawala is?
No.

00:15.683 --> 00:17.616
It's like an underground
Western Union.

00:17.685 --> 00:20.353
So, have you heard of these guys
where you got to,

00:20.421 --> 00:21.954
you know, move money
without people knowing?

00:22.023 --> 00:25.758
What you're talking about --
It's dangerous.

00:25.826 --> 00:26.959
Max: Hey.

00:27.028 --> 00:28.493
Your mom owes Uncle Max
money,

00:28.563 --> 00:31.296
but...she's not taking Uncle Max
very seriously.

00:31.298 --> 00:35.034
So go tell your mom that Max
said time's up.

00:35.102 --> 00:36.501
Don't worry.

00:36.503 --> 00:40.373
That man is never
gonna bother us again.

00:40.441 --> 00:42.441
Excuse me.
What's the deal here?

00:42.509 --> 00:44.043
You the owner?
Yeah.

00:44.111 --> 00:46.012
We got orders
to confiscate your inventory.

00:48.249 --> 00:49.848
What the hell
is this about?

00:49.917 --> 00:53.052
Well,<i> this</i> is your last chance
to save your pathetic ass.

00:53.120 --> 00:55.721
I made a phone call.
Your bar got raided.

00:55.723 --> 00:57.723
Another call next week,
it's your house.

00:57.725 --> 00:59.658
I'm the one who's gonna be
haunting your --

00:59.727 --> 01:01.194
[ Gunshot ]

01:03.865 --> 01:06.065
Dude never shuts up!

01:06.133 --> 01:08.467
The gun's a burner.

01:08.535 --> 01:12.137
But, um,
I think I'll keep it safe.

01:12.139 --> 01:13.406
Just in case.

01:14.475 --> 01:18.143
♪♪

01:18.145 --> 01:24.083
♪ She stares deeply

01:24.151 --> 01:27.887
♪ Locked inside me

01:27.955 --> 01:31.090
