02:28.015 --> 02:34.487
♪♪

02:34.555 --> 02:37.890
Jesus Christ.
I can't believe this.

02:37.958 --> 02:40.425
We got to throw him
in a dumpster somewhere.

02:40.495 --> 02:42.361
He has the Liquor Board
raid my place this morning,

02:42.429 --> 02:44.563
and he's dead
by tonight?

02:44.631 --> 02:47.432
Feds are gonna be on my ass
before the sun comes up.

02:47.434 --> 02:49.568
So then we bury him
in the desert.

02:49.636 --> 02:50.903
They'll never
find him there.

02:50.972 --> 02:52.437
Deran: Dead or missing,
it doesn't matter.

02:52.439 --> 02:53.839
I'm gonna be cuffed
and interrogated

02:53.841 --> 02:55.708
at the Federal Center
by tomorrow morning.

02:55.776 --> 02:57.242
Then just don't say shit.

02:57.312 --> 02:58.644
Chadwick's
got the gun, man.

02:58.713 --> 03:01.580
Doesn't matter. We have
the bullet that killed him.

03:01.648 --> 03:02.647
He can't connect that gun
to anything

03:02.649 --> 03:03.782
without admitting
he was here.

03:03.851 --> 03:05.184
What are you
talking about?

03:05.252 --> 03:07.652
There's blood and DNA and shit
all over the wall.

03:07.654 --> 03:09.388
We bleach.

03:09.456 --> 03:11.857
Get the mops.
You know what?

03:11.926 --> 03:14.193
Chadwick can make up
any bullshit story he wants.

03:14.261 --> 03:15.928
He's a cop.
Anybody's gonna believe him.

03:15.997 --> 03:17.796
Not gonna happen.

03:17.865 --> 03:20.265
Pope, get his car.

03:20.267 --> 03:22.001
We double wrap him.
Tight.

03:22.069 --> 03:23.336
And we bleach everything.

03:23.404 --> 03:25.604
The walls, the floor,
the ceiling -- everything.

03:25.673 --> 03:27.206
Let's go.

03:30.878 --> 03:32.512
[ Door closes ]

03:36.017 --> 03:38.251
[ Beeping ]

03:47.494 --> 03:49.962
It's an older model.
It doesn't have government tags.

03:50.031 --> 03:52.365
It's his personal car.

03:52.433 --> 03:54.167
Hopefully no GPS.

03:54.235 --> 03:56.569
His phone has GPS.
I have his phone.

03:56.637 --> 03:59.438
Turn it off
and give it to me.

03:59.506 --> 04:02.175
Are there, uh -- Are there
cameras in the alleyway?

04:02.243 --> 04:04.777
No, but there's cameras
at the restaurant

04:04.845 --> 04:06.645
on the corner
of Wisconsin and Cleveland,

04:06.714 --> 04:08.647
would've seen him
coming in.

04:08.716 --> 04:10.449
Alright, so we need
to get rid of this car,

04:10.517 --> 04:12.385
but we can't be seen
driving it.

04:16.323 --> 04:18.190
You want a truck?

04:18.259 --> 04:20.193
Yeah, how fast
can you do that?

04:20.261 --> 04:21.860
This time of night?
Pretty fast.

04:21.929 --> 04:25.197
You got one of those
American doctors in Mexico?

04:25.266 --> 04:26.265
Yeah.

04:26.333 --> 04:28.333
Good.
We're gonna need him.

04:28.335 --> 04:32.905
♪<i> 'Cause I never give up</i>
<i> and I never give in</i> ♪

04:36.543 --> 04:39.945
♪<i> Oh, so strong</i> ♪

04:39.947 --> 04:43.616
♪<i> Got the power</i>
<i> when I turn it on</i> ♪

04:43.684 --> 04:46.419
♪<i> Yeah, I'm gonna get my fill</i> ♪

04:46.487 --> 04:49.688
♪<i> Nothing's gonna stop me now</i>
<i> and nothin' ever will</i> ♪

04:49.757 --> 04:51.824
♪<i> I got the power</i> ♪

