♪♪

05:12.980 --> 05:21.386
♪♪

05:21.388 --> 05:23.322
[ Engine starts ]

05:23.390 --> 05:31.330
♪♪

05:31.398 --> 05:32.798
We're good.

05:34.669 --> 05:37.436
[ Grunts ]
Get the trunk.

05:40.141 --> 05:41.440
[ Grunts ]

05:44.345 --> 05:47.613
Oh, shit, his phone
needs to be on.

05:47.682 --> 05:48.948
And he needs
to be using it.

05:49.016 --> 05:51.550
That way he's still alive
when he leaves here.

05:51.618 --> 05:53.018
I don't have
his passcode.

05:53.087 --> 05:55.621
We get his face out.
Let's use the face recognition.

05:55.690 --> 05:57.422
Yeah, well, don't his eyes
need to be open for that?

05:57.492 --> 05:58.691
Alright, well,
open his eyes, get --

05:58.759 --> 06:01.026
I don't think it works
like that, ma--

06:01.028 --> 06:02.495
-Is that thumb recognition?
-Yeah, okay.

06:02.563 --> 06:04.363
-Well, get his hand out.
-Use his hand.

06:04.431 --> 06:05.698
Get his hand.

06:11.105 --> 06:13.372
-[ Grunts ]
-Alright.

06:15.376 --> 06:17.510
Alright, I'll just
keep it unlocked.

06:17.578 --> 06:19.845
-Good.
-He's got mail.

06:19.914 --> 06:22.781
Alright, well, respond.
Something generic.

06:22.850 --> 06:25.384
-Quickly.
-Alright, here you go.

06:25.452 --> 06:26.785
Alright, let's go.
Close it.

06:26.854 --> 06:28.854
Alright,
meet back at the spot.

06:28.923 --> 06:30.723
Yeah, yeah, stay off Cleveland,
alright?

06:30.791 --> 06:32.791
The cameras cannot see
your car there, alright?

06:32.860 --> 06:34.727
And burn that shirt.
It's got blood all over it.

06:34.795 --> 06:37.196
-Yeah.
-We got this. Let's go.

06:37.264 --> 06:40.265
♪♪

06:40.267 --> 06:43.135
♪<i> Machines are racing</i> ♪

06:43.204 --> 06:45.871
♪<i> The body's aching</i> ♪

06:45.873 --> 06:48.741
♪<i> The gas tops over</i> ♪

06:48.809 --> 06:51.544
♪<i> A silent soldier</i> ♪

06:51.612 --> 06:54.279
♪<i> We're always ready</i> ♪

06:54.281 --> 06:56.349
♪<i> The system's steady</i> ♪

06:56.417 --> 06:58.818
♪<i> Let's go</i> ♪

07:02.690 --> 07:05.558
♪<i> Words are floating</i> ♪

07:05.626 --> 07:08.493
♪<i> My mind's eroding</i> ♪

07:08.563 --> 07:11.164
♪<i> There's no complaining</i> ♪

07:11.232 --> 07:14.433
♪<i> Its always raining</i> ♪

07:14.501 --> 07:17.502
Oh, come on.

07:17.572 --> 07:19.238
He's got everybody.

07:19.306 --> 07:21.707
♪<i> Let's go</i> ♪

07:29.384 --> 07:31.884
[ Car door opens, closes ]

07:34.655 --> 07:36.455
You got the money?

07:36.523 --> 07:38.925
Yeah.
And two burners.

07:41.062 --> 07:42.528
Phones off.

07:52.940 --> 07:58.811
♪♪

07:58.880 --> 08:02.481
[ Truck door opens, closes ]

08:02.549 --> 08:05.017
[ Truck door closes,
engine starts ]

08:07.422 --> 08:09.622
Craig: You can't trust
the cops, man.

08:13.294 --> 08:15.227
Shit happens, alright?

08:15.296 --> 08:23.035
♪♪

08:23.104 --> 08:30.843
♪♪

